'''CenturyTel of Mountain Home, Inc.''' is a telephone operating of [[CenturyLink]] providing local telephone services to communities in [[Arkansas]], including [[Mountain Home, Arkansas|Mountain Home]]. The company was founded in [[1946]].
The company has been owned by [[CenturyLink]], which was formerly CenturyTel.
